<i>Gyu-cheol. let's say</i>

756
00:55:38.418 --> 00:55:42.339
your parole hearing goes well
and you're released back into society.

757
00:55:43.214 --> 00:55:45.008
What would you want to do most?

758
00:55:49.054 --> 00:55:50.055
<i>I'm not sure.</i>

759
00:55:50.764 --> 00:55:52.807
<i>I don't even dare hope for it.</i>

760
00:55:54.351 --> 00:55:57.896
But if it were possible…

761
00:56:00.940 --> 00:56:03.151
I'd want to go back to school.

762
00:56:05.570 --> 00:56:08.281
WILL I EVER BE ABLE TO… FORGIVE GYU-CHEOL?

763
00:56:08.365 --> 00:56:09.657
<i>Based on witness statements</i>

764
00:56:09.741 --> 00:56:14.871
<i>that the defendant. Cho Gyu-cheol.</i>
<i>showed ongoing hostility toward Ms. Choi.</i>

765
00:56:14.954 --> 00:56:19.042
we seek ten years' imprisonment
for premeditated retaliatory murder.

766
00:56:20.001 --> 00:56:21.252
It is clear

767
00:56:21.336 --> 00:56:23.713
Cho Gyu-cheol was changing
under Ms. Choi's guidance.

768
00:56:24.381 --> 00:56:27.550
This was nothing more
than a deeply unfortunate accident.

769
00:56:43.525 --> 00:56:44.484
Get on now.

770
00:57:59.934 --> 00:58:02.896
